 <title>About This Guide</title>

 <para>
  &sles4sapreg; is the reference platform for the software development of &sap;.
  It is optimized for &sap; applications.
  <phrase condition="noquick">
  This document provides detailed information about installing and
  customizing &sles4sap;.
  </phrase>
  <phrase condition="quick">
  This document guides you through the installation of &sles4sap;.
  </phrase>
 </para>
 <para>
  &sleha; is also part of &sles4sap;.
 </para>

 <sect1 condition="noquick">
  <title>Overview</title>

  <para>
   The &sles4sap; Guide is divided into the following chapters:
  </para>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha-about" xrefstyle="select:title,nopage"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      An overview of &sles4sap;.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha-plan" xrefstyle="select:title,nopage"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Information on hardware requirements, the installation workflow,
      partitioning, and other installation planning aspects.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha-install" xrefstyle="select:title,nopage"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Installing the &sls; operating system that forms the basis of
      &sles4sap;.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha-install-sap" xrefstyle="select:title,nopage"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Installing &sap; applications on &sles4sap;, either directly after the
      installation of the operating system or in a running system.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha-serve-mediaset" xrefstyle="select:title,nopage"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Setting up a server for all &instmedia; used within your organization.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="sec-component" xrefstyle="select:title,nopage"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Description of tools to configure &sles4sap;.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>

